#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc177"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts177"></a>
msgctxt "thag2.29:5.1"
msgid "“Nadanti evaṃ sappaññā,"
msgstr "This is how the wise roar:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.29:5.2"
msgid "sīhāva girigabbhare;"
msgstr "Like lions in mountain caves,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.29:5.3"
msgid "Vīrā vijitasaṅgāmā,"
msgstr "Heroes, triumphant in battle,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.29:5.4"
msgid "jetvā māraṃ <span class=\"var\" title=\"savāhanaṃ (si, s2, s3, pts1-2)\" id=\"note113\">savāhiniṃ</span>."
msgstr "Having vanquished Māra and his army."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc178"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts178"></a>
msgctxt "thag2.29:6.1"
msgid "Satthā ca pariciṇṇo me,"
msgstr "I’ve attended on the teacher;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.29:6.2"
msgid "dhammo saṃgho ca pūjito;"
msgstr "I’ve honoured the Dhamma and the Saṅgha;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.29:6.3"
msgid "Ahañca vitto sumano,"
msgstr "I’m happy and joyful,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag2.29:6.4"
msgid "puttaṃ disvā anāsavan”ti."
msgstr "Because I’ve seen my son free of defilements."

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
